data.description: This 3 bedroom home in Kearsley school district is an excellent choice for anyone seeking a comfortable and cozy home. As soon as you enter, you will be greeted by a spacious living room that boasts great natural lighting, making it an ideal space for relaxation and enjoyment. The hardwood flooring throughout the home adds a touch of elegance and sophistication to the atmosphere. One of the key highlights of this property is the large basement that can be used as an additional living space, storage area or entertaining guests. The spacious partially fenced in backyard provides ample room for family play or hosting get togethers with friends and family. Whether you are a young family looking for a place to call home or an individual looking for a comfortable and well-maintained property, this 3 bedroom house in Kearsley school district is definitely worth a closer look.
